    {
      "id": "k5KZiJBTeq6IQSoZFmKsi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -298.74609375,
      "y": 2339.234375,
      "width": 783.2994995117188,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 119101798,
      "version": 364,
      "versionNonce": 6027066,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784789831505,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n    - Read only filesystems(write any o/p to temporary directory)\n    - Cpu and Memory bounds\n    - Explicit timeout per execution\n    - VPC for network controls\n    - no system calls(Seccomp)\n\nWe'd use docker containers while limiting network access, \nsetting CPU and memory bounds, and enforcing a timeout on the code execution",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\n    - Read only filesystems(write any o/p to temporary directory)\n    - Cpu and Memory bounds\n    - Explicit timeout per execution\n    - VPC for network controls\n    - no system calls(Seccomp)\n\nWe'd use docker containers while limiting network access, \nsetting CPU and memory bounds, and enforcing a timeout on the code execution",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PoblvFIELQyEqjbgMVr_y",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -309.90721648672337,
      "y": 2640.21484375,
      "width": 736.3617962546967,
      "height": 30.988281250000004,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 351688506,
      "version": 74,
      "versionNonce": 1510661798,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784728058021,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. How would you make fetching the leaderboard more efficient?",
      "fontSize": 26.946331521739122,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. How would you make fetching the leaderboard more efficient?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "AKfbVEovX3dUonmPqMd_B",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -254.123291015625,
      "y": 2690.8203125,
      "width": 758.87939453125,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 583218746,
      "version": 107,
      "versionNonce": 1132774522,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784724383155,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Instead of calculating the leaderboard from millions of submissions every time\nsomeone requests it, we calculate it once when each submission arrives and\nkeep the latest ranking in Redis",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Instead of calculating the leaderboard from millions of submissions every time someone requests it, we calculate it once when each submission arrives and keep the latest ranking in Redis",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "RZAbo46al-lfc8dOIfG_h",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -255,
      "y": 2799.125,
      "width": 691.259521484375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1045018490,
      "version": 8,
      "versionNonce": 623053286,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784793101368,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Instead of computing the leaderboard every time, \nupdate the leaderboard immediately whenever a submission is accepted.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Instead of computing the leaderboard every time, \nupdate the leaderboard immediately whenever a submission is accepted.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FmDDkB5df6YW4S1Ekw-O6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -251,
      "y": 2884.125,
      "width": 358.09979248046875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1909546554,
      "version": 49,
      "versionNonce": 1719823546,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784792725162,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "store it in Redis sorted set(ZSET).",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "store it in Redis sorted set(ZSET).",
