      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784793110405,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "GET /competitions/:competitionId/leaderboard?top=100",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "GET /competitions/:competitionId/leaderboard?top=100",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Odp2FW82YF4DYW_gVploU",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -215.48638916015625,
      "y": 5676.71484375,
      "width": 741.1993408203125,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b10",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 654093606,
      "version": 72,
      "versionNonce": 1652932838,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784793325252,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The Redis sorted set uses a \nkey -> competition:leaderboard:{competitionId}, \n-> score being the user's total score or solve time, and \n-> value being the userId. \n\nWe'd implement an API endpoint like \nGET /competitions/:competitionId/leaderboard?top=100.\n\nWhen processing a submission, we'd update Redis with a command like \n\nZADD competition:leaderboard:{competitionId} {score} {userId}",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The Redis sorted set uses a \nkey -> competition:leaderboard:{competitionId}, \n-> score being the user's total score or solve time, and \n-> value being the userId. \n\nWe'd implement an API endpoint like \nGET /competitions/:competitionId/leaderboard?top=100.\n\nWhen processing a submission, we'd update Redis with a command like \n\nZADD competition:leaderboard:{competitionId} {score} {userId}",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FUHkw3OVts0qTaPderB9A",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -210,
      "y": 5983,
      "width": 736.6795654296875,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b11",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1800340154,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 1010044538,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784793350667,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "To retrieve the top N users, we'd use \nZRANGE competition:leaderboard:{competitionId} 0 N-1 REV WITHSCORES",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "To retrieve the top N users, we'd use \nZRANGE competition:leaderboard:{competitionId} 0 N-1 REV WITHSCORES",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
